<strong>Car type: </strong>Larger and heavier vehicles, such as trucks and <a href="https://rapidautoshipping.com/blogs/suv-auto-transport" target="_blank"><strong>SUVs</strong></a>, are more expensive to move. Modifications that lower the car or demand more clearance may raise the transportation cost.
