<strong>Transport type:</strong> Open automobile transport is the most cost-effective mode of vehicle delivery. <a href="https://rapidautoshipping.com/services/enclosed-shipping" target="_blank"><strong>Enclosed transportation</strong></a> is a fantastic alternative for a premium or vintage automobiles since it protects them from road debris and weather conditions, but it can cost up to 40% extra.
<br><br>
<strong>Time of year:</strong> Auto shipping demand spikes between January and July, making it more expensive to move a car during certain months.
